Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.68,0:00:05.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多要講的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.14,0:00:08.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於她的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:10.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於他的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.58,0:00:12.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於他的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.84,0:00:15.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於她的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.30,0:00:17.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於它的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.72,0:00:19.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.29,0:00:21.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有他的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.78,0:00:25.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是從這裏開始太過突然
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.81,0:00:27.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我按照順序一一講述吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:02.90,tk-title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz354.174\pos(342,199)}鄰座的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.93,0:02:02.90,tk-title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz357.51\pos(186,248)}吉田君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.81,0:02:05.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做水谷雫
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.23,0:02:07.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,松陽高校一年級生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.25,0:02:12.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鄰座的吉田同學從入學第一天引發流血事件後
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.15,0:02:14.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一次都沒來過學校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.00,0:02:22.89,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽說在一片血泊中狂笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.30,0:02:24.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田春被當成夢幻新生
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.15,0:02:27.27,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在也依然成為學校最熱門的話題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.92,0:02:28.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個月前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:32.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他把高年級學生打到送醫院的事發現場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.51,0:02:38.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在依然清晰地殘留著凄慘的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.30,0:02:41.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這對我來說根本無關緊要
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.16,0:02:44.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該買新的參考書了
