Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.31,0:02:47.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有一個夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.42,0:02:50.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了達成那個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.11,0:02:54.81,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我唯一感興趣的就只有微積分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.06,0:02:56.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有時間管別人的閒事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.27,0:02:58.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.25,0:03:05.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.34,0:03:08.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫做水谷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.97,0:03:10.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.55,0:03:12.13,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.30,0:03:15.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你 馬克才會死掉的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.06,0:03:16.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.22,0:03:19.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告訴過你不要在店裏鬧的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.67,0:03:21.80,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是阿三哥 都怪他
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.91,0:03:24.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克的死怨不得別人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.15,0:03:25.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪你自己技術不佳
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.68,0:03:26.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先不提那個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.03,0:03:27.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人找你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.97,0:03:28.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 請收下這個
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:44.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師叫我送過來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:46.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:02.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 是學校派來的走狗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.49,0:04:03.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.19,0:04:04.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少裝傻了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:05.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疼 好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.91,0:04:07.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是來送講義的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.88,0:04:08.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,講義？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.39,0:04:12.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒騙我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:20.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還以為是像那個女老師一樣來勸我上學的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.73,0:04:21.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什麼名字
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.45,0:04:25.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水…水谷雫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.64,0:04:28.27,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 雫呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這就是那個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.04,0:04:32.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為感冒在家休息
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:36.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友送講義過來那種
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.75,0:04:38.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我春就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:40.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我們是朋友嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.90,0:04:44.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.98,0:04:45.93,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.19,0:04:47.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:49.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對他只有這種印象
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.75,0:04:52.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要信守承諾哦 冱子老師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.93,0:04:55.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說只要我幫你跑腿就替我買參考書的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:58.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你哦水谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.04,0:05:01.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他都不肯見我 好難辦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.63,0:05:02.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.35,0:05:05.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被他當成朋友了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.58,0:05:07.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.42,0:05:10.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你能說服他來學校嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.57,0:05:11.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說服？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.96,0:05:16.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田他早就解除停學的處罰了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.12,0:05:19.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有些做過火
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.44,0:05:21.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錯主要在高年級學生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.43,0:05:26.27,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二話不說就做停學處理
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.45,0:05:29.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他對學校非常的不信任呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:32.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此而拒絕上學是不是有點可惜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.28,0:05:35.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去說服他吧 好不好 水谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.29,0:05:37.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.22,0:05:38.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.86,0:05:40.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好為難的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.27,0:05:42.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要我自己去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.19,0:05:45.66,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能啦 絕對不可能 不可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.96,0:05:44.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什麼玩笑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要再去接觸那種人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.80,0:05:58.55,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:00.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敢喊就侵犯你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.15,0:06:02.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.19,0:06:07.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:11.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:13.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你帶我到這裏幹嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.82,0:06:15.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在來的途中發現了一條流浪犬
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.26,0:06:17.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把它藏到這裏了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.99,0:06:18.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.28,0:06:20.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.37,0:06:22.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.89,0:06:23.78,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:25.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對狗…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.52,0:06:28.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒不如說是我不擅長和動物相處
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.46,0:06:30.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.26,0:06:33.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它死了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.15,0:06:35.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 咪咪它真是幸福吶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.15,0:06:38.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和大家成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.53,0:06:40.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了水谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.39,0:06:42.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有作業要寫
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.87,0:06:44.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓我回去了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.50,0:06:51.06,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後的一段時間同學們都叫我「乾冰」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.79,0:06:53.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這也是沒辦法的事情嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.55,0:06:55.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當時真的沒有覺得傷心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.24,0:06:57.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈哈 找到了 找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.96,0:07:00.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在等著我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:03.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這傢伙 嘴裏真臭啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.74,0:07:07.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大概不是流浪犬啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.09,0:07:11.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾經周折 總算是把狗還給主人了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.46,0:07:17.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會來這裏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.97,0:07:21.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有這些人 是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.61,0:07:22.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 春
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.14,0:07:24.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 山賢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.73,0:07:25.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.73,0:07:27.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是我朋友雫
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.42,0:07:28.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.56,0:07:32.84,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說春 能借點錢給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.03,0:07:34.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.39,0:07:36.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前段時間發生了事情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.29,0:07:38.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,零花錢被停掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:42.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你啦 我們是朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.14,0:07:47.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人 是笨蛋啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.89,0:07:57.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.45,0:08:00.36,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.60,0:08:03.43,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你今天去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.45,0:08:04.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那又怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.57,0:08:09.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺…覺得開心嗎 學校
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.04,0:08:13.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.52,0:08:17.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就像是放學後和朋友一起玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.37,0:08:22.88,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田 難道說你很想去學校…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.32,0:08:27.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這麼想知道的話就來上學嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.04,0:08:31.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.35,0:08:35.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道為什麼 大家都害怕我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.44,0:08:38.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等我察覺的時候 他們都已躲得遠遠的了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.27,0:08:41.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就不想去學校了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.00,0:08:47.94,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是到我家來的 雫你是第一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.20,0:08:50.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的那群傢伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.85,0:08:54.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一群不害怕我願意和我一起玩的人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:57.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以就算不去學校也無所謂了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:01.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得會這麼想的也只有吉田你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.25,0:09:06.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果是朋友的話就不會敲詐你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.73,0:09:09.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我不太瞭解你們之間的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.97,0:09:13.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是像那種朋友還不如不要的好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:28.66,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個討厭的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.41,0:09:45.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這算什麼男人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.41,0:09:48.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是說了真心話而已嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.16,0:09:51.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然會這麼生氣…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.22,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水谷同學
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.17,0:09:58.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你勸他來學校了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.75,0:10:03.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 連電話也不接了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.94,0:10:07.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再這樣下去 果然只有退學了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.50,0:10:13.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.62,0:10:14.66,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春不在喲
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.97,0:10:18.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不是 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.58,0:10:22.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果吉田再不來學校就會被退學的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.51,0:10:24.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能替我轉達一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.36,0:10:28.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.40,0:10:30.23,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.58,0:10:33.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來玩一發麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.76,0:10:39.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打不中
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.82,0:10:41.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我會來玩這個
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是不來的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.77,0:10:46.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的春那傢伙到底是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.05,0:10:49.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近他完全不借錢給我了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.44,0:10:51.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嘛 那也無所謂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.97,0:10:53.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們又不是沒有錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.83,0:10:55.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說和他一起很沒勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.90,0:10:58.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都覺得已經沒有必要理他了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.08,0:11:01.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 所以和你說了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.70,0:11:02.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.06,0:11:10.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.28,0:11:13.74,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙不也有正常人的感覺嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.03,0:11:20.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 反正和我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.40,0:11:24.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後說他的狗被誘拐了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.36,0:11:25.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.50,0:11:27.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我 有點奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.92,0:11:33.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.91,0:11:34.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.02,0:11:36.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要為他做這些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:36.43,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:38.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是春上次帶著的女人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:41.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是看到他那副表情的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.42,0:11:45.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉…吉田
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.59,0:11:48.66,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是打心底認為你們是他的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.65,0:11:50.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.01,0:11:53.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你們也是這麼想的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.22,0:11:57.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和春…更加真誠的交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.63,0:12:02.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.91,0:12:07.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 春！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.22,0:12:12.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們這些傢伙 今天給我滾回去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.35,0:12:24.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉田同學沉默著送我走在回家的路上
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.55,0:12:30.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這沒有什麼好哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.29,0:12:33.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.79,0:12:35.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是覺得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.77,0:12:37.68,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.56,0:12:42.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那種時候都不會掉一滴淚的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.07,0:12:44.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有種想哭的衝動
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.50,0:12:52.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.74,0:12:57.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快春的身邊就會有很多人陪伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.98,0:13:12.26,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有你的話 我願意試著去上學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.22,0:13:14.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣就太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.96,0:13:16.87,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點小鹿亂撞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.19,0:13:19.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…或許喜歡上雫了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:23.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 那是指朋友的意思嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.31,0:13:24.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,性方面的意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.42,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:29.54,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那大概是雛鳥情節吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:32.71,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒有其他朋友產生了錯覺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:38.94,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼我交到朋友的話就沒問題了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.30,0:13:42.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.36,0:13:45.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也不會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:47.66,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.38,0:13:49.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.70,0:13:53.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在某個美麗晴朗的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.47,0:13:56.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有生以來第一次被男生告白了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.59,0:14:02.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天 吉田真的來上學了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.77,0:14:06.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫！我的腳站麻了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.98,0:14:08.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在這裏幹什麼呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.20,0:14:11.44,setting2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(179,262)}{\fad(50,0)}一個月後
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.79,0:14:11.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.96,0:14:13.08,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.40,0:14:14.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們要敲詐啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.58,0:14:16.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些傢伙突然說要我把錢交出來
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.10,0:14:18.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.74,0:14:21.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這是去哪裏？雫
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:23.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去上體育課啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.43,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.53,0:14:28.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於…不過 這也是很普通的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.21,0:14:31.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,豁出去了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.11,0:14:38.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.47,0:14:40.29,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？但是阿三哥說…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.64,0:14:42.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這一個月
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:45.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有著對學校先入為主的錯誤印象
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.72,0:14:49.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春的行徑古怪難以捉摸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.88,0:14:50.66,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.89,0:14:53.59,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎樣都不關我的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.22,0:14:55.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,問題是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.80,0:14:57.05,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶我去吃這個
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.45,0:14:58.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.54,0:15:01.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？這個可是文字燒呀！文字燒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.35,0:15:02.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經說了很多次了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.03,0:15:05.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後要好好學習！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.66,0:15:06.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.23,0:15:10.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從他來到學校就一直纏著我不放
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.77,0:15:12.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,害我不能用心讀書
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.64,0:15:14.61,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是水谷同學嗎 誒！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:17.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！你在看什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.29,0:15:18.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇她
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.74,0:15:21.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭你！給我閃遠點
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.06,0:15:23.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.99,0:15:26.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停…停！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吉…吉田同學 要好好的呵護女同學
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把老師心愛的書借給你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.39,0:15:34.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好相處哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:36.35,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.60,0:15:42.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的手溫柔的抱住我 我不禁心跳加速
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.57,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使這樣也不會變的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:52.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定是喜歡你的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.60,0:15:58.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這到底是怎麼回事 我想了又想
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.01,0:16:01.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師！要怎麼呵護女生？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.56,0:16:03.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該就是體貼她吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.91,0:16:05.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那要怎麼體貼勒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.22,0:16:08.93,tk-default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是溫柔的對待吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.21,0:16:11.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次放棄了沒有解開的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.70,0:16:16.75,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些傢伙看起來很開心吶
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.30,0:16:21.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下應該是去吃飯或者玩躲避球吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.75,0:16:23.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好呢 可以做這些事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.63,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶！雫！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.80,0:16:27.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了不去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.35,0:16:29.77,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就是期中考試了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.08,0:16:33.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不是單純的想吃文字燒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.66,0:16:37.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一般好朋友的話 不是會放學後去別的地方逛逛嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.11,0:16:40.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和雫一起去啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.19,0:16:44.07,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除了雫之外 根本沒有人正眼看我
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:48.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰叫你動不動就瞪人家恐嚇別人 甚至還會暴走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有新生代表致辭嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.55,0:16:55.81,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓入學考試的第一名來擔任的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.27,0:16:58.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.46,0:17:00.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有在學習這件事從沒有輸給過別人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.20,0:17:03.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了不輸 我一直非常努力
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.31,0:17:05.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來請新生代表致辭
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.32,0:17:06.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是致辭的人…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.96,0:17:09.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並不是我
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.79,0:17:14.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.49,0:17:17.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次期中考試一定不能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.50,0:17:20.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在不是吃文字燒的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.97,0:17:24.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！這個要先求出交點的坐標
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.46,0:17:31.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有 這裏錯了哦 b不是等於8而是等於4
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.55,0:17:33.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.85,0:17:37.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天新生代表…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點到前面來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:41.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.69,0:17:44.28,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新生代表 吉田春
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:46.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.49,0:17:51.39,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.60,0:17:53.98,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你昨天為什麼擅自跑回去了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:17:57.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.00,0:17:58.99,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.51,0:18:02.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 期中考之前你都是我的對手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.91,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請不要再妨礙我學習了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.16,0:18:10.89,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學習算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.85,0:18:14.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有答案的東西 必然很簡單啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.72,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就這麼討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.69,0:18:24.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.12,0:18:28.70,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我的心情非得變得這麼差
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.74,0:18:33.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去學習吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.44,0:18:37.02,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 和別人無關
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:39.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直以來都是這麼走過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.87,0:18:44.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.72,0:18:45.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:46.79,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.06,0:18:48.43,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.74,0:18:50.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我剛剛看到她了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.20,0:18:54.45,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 把她帶過來做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.84,0:18:56.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為很不甘心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.84,0:18:58.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被一年級打成那個樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.33,0:19:00.04,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛 一年級的？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.12,0:19:01.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要吃零食嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.06,0:19:06.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些人是 之前敲詐被春揍過的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.12,0:19:10.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 可以讓我學習嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.43,0:19:12.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請便
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.63,0:19:17.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 自從和他扯上關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.12,0:19:18.85,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切全都亂套了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.51,0:19:24.48,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是…想靜下心來學習而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.97,0:19:27.62,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫 在哪裏？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.23,0:19:30.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.08,0:19:33.15,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們 對雫做了什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.16,0:19:34.81,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 我們回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.82,0:19:36.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能算了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:38.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要宰了你們
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.96,0:19:41.17,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的沒有事的 你住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.18,0:19:42.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩死了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.76,0:19:51.41,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…喂 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.17,0:19:55.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.15,0:19:58.09,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受夠了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.00,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們絕交吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.05,0:20:06.37,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再陪你玩朋友遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.53,0:20:09.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我眼前消失
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.64,0:20:13.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想你一定只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.16,0:20:17.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想在我身上尋找羈絆這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.18,0:20:20.82,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起 我不能回應這種感情
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.78,0:20:25.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不覺得我有這種價值
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.15,0:20:31.21,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
