Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.22,0:20:59.16,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.91,0:21:00.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.16,0:21:04.27,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.34,0:21:06.69,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是第一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:09.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明應該高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.44,0:21:15.25,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 除了當冤大頭和打架之外
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.26,0:21:17.05,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不會做點別的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.54,0:21:19.31,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前陣子交的那些傢伙們也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.39,0:21:22.30,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請和春…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.49,0:21:24.90,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更加真誠的交朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:33.10,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.44,0:21:35.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.73,0:21:37.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.55,0:21:41.73,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特意過來和我說這件事 就這麼討厭我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.56,0:21:44.67,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.36,0:21:48.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…不討厭你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.59,0:21:53.96,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這沒有什麼好哭的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.44,0:21:57.14,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 我是覺得很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.62,0:22:03.27,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個時候 確實感覺到了自己心中的震動
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.63,0:22:06.83,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,忘記說了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.47,0:22:10.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前謝謝你過來救我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.38,0:22:12.24,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.24,0:22:15.18,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:21.03,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近 大家一致認為吉田春變得特別溫馴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.41,0:22:26.53,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你今天很安靜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.49,0:22:28.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.91,0:22:31.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你…雖然不是很明白
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.52,0:22:32.86,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很重視學習不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.57,0:22:36.49,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你重視的事情 我也會重視的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.59,0:22:39.40,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:42.38,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呵護 就是這個意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:48.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊 我現在…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:50.32,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在被他呵護著嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.67,0:22:55.52,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 不學習了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.21,0:22:57.92,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚…肚子餓了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.51,0:23:04.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,文字燒 文字燒 文字燒…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.20,0:23:06.51,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然學到一半就停了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.52,0:23:08.56,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可見肚子真的很餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.84,0:23:13.12,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧 再說 也學不進去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.64,0:23:17.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你看起來很開心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.83,0:23:22.60,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.49,0:23:38.65,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 沒有心跳加速的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.00,0:23:40.95,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇怪 為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.33,0:23:43.01,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,前些天就覺得了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.02,0:23:45.20,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對你完全沒有心跳加速的感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.75,0:23:48.34,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:51.64,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明之前還那麼心跳加速的說
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.64,0:23:54.76,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我還是很喜歡你哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.42,0:23:59.97,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們快點走吧 雫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:11.58,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是雞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.59,0:24:12.44,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 你是野生的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.76,0:24:13.47,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.57,0:24:16.11,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦 被雨淋濕會感冒的哦 進來
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.52,0:24:18.50,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不願意嗎 我昨天洗過澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.51,0:24:19.46,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好痛 好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.47,0:24:20.19,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爪子 爪子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.20,0:24:21.33,tk-default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那裏是重要部位…
